profile_positions.description:
After the SABMiller/ABInBev combination, I was appointed to Director: Synergies & Integration to lead the post merger integration program. Highlights:

•	led the cross-functional team responsible for the carve out of SABMiller global brands and all associated operations in Africa and transitioned these  businesses to the new global owners;
•	led the delivery of the ABInBev/SABMiller Integration & Synergies program resulting in hundreds of millions of US Dollars in cost savings for the Africa zone which exceeded expectations in both 2017 full year and quarter 1 2018 results as published in the 2017 annual and 2018 Q1 financial reports.
